data.description: You will love the location and size! Spacious Cape Cod with many possibilities. As you enter the desirable floor plan offering a very spacious h/w floored living room, separate tile floored walk way to the down stairs bedroom that also boasts an illuminating slider that leads out to a deck. Next is the full bath and around to the new spacious kitchen that opens to the dining room which is equipped with ez close cabinets and drawers! Off the kitchen is entry into a HUGE, illuminating great room which includes your utility area. The sliders offer you a great view of your own in ground swimming pool! The property is fully fenced in to keep safe little ones and pets. Custom pavers make poolside entertaining luxurious. The second floor gives you a huge and sprawling Main Bedroom including a 3-pc bath-suite and large walk-in closet connected by a comfortable sitting room. 2 additional large bedrooms complete the upstairs with a large shared hallway bath. All bedrooms boast large closets. This large home offers lots of living space. The back part of the property has been cleared to offer more use of this large rectangular lot. This home has so much to offer just needs a little TLC! Hurry and make this home yours today! Owner is licensed Delaware real estate agent.
